<h2>Don't Forget Your Manners</h2>

<p>Introductions first! Don't Lose Your Game is a tool to help you run your game of Don't Rest Your Head.</p>

<p>It will roll the dice, separated into discipline, exhaustion, madness and pain and determine who won (either the player or pain) and which pool dominated. Furthermore, it will manage the pools of despair and hope generated by the game’s mechanics.</p>

<p>All you need to do is <%= link_to "sign up", new_user_registration_path %> and don’t rest your head!</p>

